oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Artist in Residence - Rosanne Cash - 2015-09-03
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Second of three Artist in Residence performances by Rosanne Cash from the CMA Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on September 3, 2015. Special guest include Emmylou Harris and Lucinda Williams.
